            "content": "# Packages overview\n\n**Active contributors:** Alvin Sng, Andrei Savin, Luke Alvoeiro, Nikita Lilichenko, factory-sherry, factory-octavian, David Vendrow, Ricky S\n\n## Purpose\n\nThe `packages/` workspace contains shared libraries consumed by the apps (`apps/web`, `apps/desktop`, `apps/backend`, `apps/daemon`, `apps/cli`). Each package is an npm workspace with `\"private\": true` and exposes named export paths. Packages never import from `apps/`; the dependency flow is strictly one-directional.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/\n├── common/           # Shared types, API contracts, enums (@factory/common)\n├── core-ui/          # Design system and primitives (@factory/core-ui)\n├── droid-core/       # AI agent core: tools, LLMs, streaming (@factory/droid-core)\n├── frontend/         # Shared React feature modules (@factory/frontend)\n├── component-library/ # Chat UI, diff viewer, Mermaid, markdown (@factory/component-library)\n├── daemon-client/    # WebSocket client for daemon JSON-RPC (@factory/daemon-client)\n├── daemon-core/      # Core daemon logic: sessions, relay, terminal (@factory/daemon-core)\n├── droid-sdk/        # TypeScript SDK for driving droid exec processes (@factory/droid-sdk)\n├── environment/      # Typed environment variable resolution (@factory/environment)\n├── eslint-config/    # Shared ESLint configuration (@factory/eslint-config)\n├── logging/          # Logging, metrics, Sentry, OpenTelemetry (@factory/logging)\n├── mcp/              # Empty placeholder (MCP tooling lives in utils/mcp)\n├── models/           # Firestore/data model definitions (@factory/models)\n├── runtime/          # Auth utilities (WorkOS, token refresh) (@factory/runtime)\n├── services/         # External service adapters: Firebase, AWS, Stripe, Slack (@factory/services)\n├── signal-core/      # Signal definitions for analytics pipeline (@factory/signal-core)\n├── test-utils/       # Shared test mocks and helpers (@factory/test-utils)\n├── ui/               # Empty placeholder\n├── updater/          # CLI/desktop auto-update logic (@factory/updater)\n└── utils/            # Pure utility functions (@factory/utils)\n```\n\n## Dependency hierarchy\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    common[\"@factory/common\"]\n    environment[\"@factory/environment\"]\n    utils[\"@factory/utils\"]\n    logging[\"@factory/logging\"]\n    models[\"@factory/models\"]\n    services[\"@factory/services\"]\n    runtime[\"@factory/runtime\"]\n    droid_core[\"@factory/droid-core\"]\n    daemon_client[\"@factory/daemon-client\"]\n    daemon_core[\"@factory/daemon-core\"]\n    droid_sdk[\"@factory/droid-sdk\"]\n    core_ui[\"@factory/core-ui\"]\n    component_library[\"@factory/component-library\"]\n    frontend[\"@factory/frontend\"]\n    signal_core[\"@factory/signal-core\"]\n\n    common --> environment\n    utils --> common\n    logging --> utils\n    logging --> common\n    models --> common\n    services --> common\n    services --> environment\n    services --> logging\n    services --> utils\n    runtime --> common\n    runtime --> environment\n    runtime --> logging\n    runtime --> models\n    runtime --> services\n    runtime --> utils\n    droid_core --> common\n    droid_core --> logging\n    droid_core --> models\n    droid_core --> services\n    droid_core --> utils\n    daemon_client --> common\n    droid_sdk --> common\n    droid_sdk --> logging\n    droid_sdk --> utils\n    daemon_core --> common\n    daemon_core --> logging\n    daemon_core --> models\n    daemon_core --> runtime\n    daemon_core --> services\n    daemon_core --> utils\n    daemon_core --> droid_sdk\n    core_ui --> common\n    component_library --> common\n    component_library --> core_ui\n    component_library --> droid_core\n    component_library --> logging\n    component_library --> utils\n    frontend --> common\n    frontend --> core_ui\n    frontend --> daemon_client\n    frontend --> logging\n```\n\n## Key abstractions\n\n| Package | Import path | Primary role |\n|---------|-------------|--------------|\n| `@factory/common` | `@factory/common/<domain>` | Canonical types and enums shared across every layer |\n| `@factory/core-ui` | `@factory/core-ui` | Design system — mandatory for all web UI |\n| `@factory/droid-core` | `@factory/droid-core/<module>` | Tool definitions, LLM providers, streaming protocol |\n| `@factory/frontend` | `@factory/frontend` | React app shell and feature modules |\n| `@factory/component-library` | `@factory/component-library` | Chat, diff, Mermaid, markdown rendering components |\n| `@factory/daemon-client` | `@factory/daemon-client` | WebSocket JSON-RPC client to `factoryd` |\n| `@factory/daemon-core` | `@factory/daemon-core` | Daemon session orchestration, relay, terminal |\n| `@factory/droid-sdk` | `@factory/droid-sdk` | SDK for driving droid exec from external processes |\n| `@factory/services` | `@factory/services/<provider>` | Firebase, AWS, Stripe, Slack, WorkOS adapters |\n| `@factory/runtime` | `@factory/runtime/auth` | Token management, WorkOS auth flows |\n| `@factory/models` | `@factory/models` | Firestore document schemas |\n| `@factory/logging` | `@factory/logging` | Pino logger, metrics, Sentry, OpenTelemetry |\n| `@factory/environment` | `@factory/environment` | Typed env-var parsing with provider injection |\n| `@factory/utils` | `@factory/utils/<module>` | Pure utilities: formatting, LLM helpers, fuzzy search |\n| `@factory/updater` | `@factory/updater` | Semver-based auto-update for CLI and desktop |\n| `@factory/signal-core` | `@factory/signal-core/<module>` | Signal schemas for analytics batch pipeline |\n| `@factory/eslint-config` | dev only | Shared ESLint rules |\n| `@factory/test-utils` | dev only | Shared test mocks |\n\n## How it works\n\nAll packages use TypeScript source directly (no build step for package-to-package consumption). Each package declares named export paths in its `\"exports\"` field in `package.json`. Consumers import via the published path (e.g. `import { Box } from '@factory/core-ui'` or `import { SessionPrivacyLevel } from '@factory/common/session'`).\n\nTurborepo handles task ordering: `typecheck` and `test` depend on upstream packages being typechecked first. The `build` script, where it exists, generates CSS tokens or similar artifacts.\n\n## Usage guidelines\n\n- **Web/desktop UI code**: import from `@factory/core-ui` for primitives, `@factory/component-library` for higher-level chat/diff components, `@factory/frontend` for feature modules. Never use raw `<div>`, `<button>`, or `<input>`.\n- **Shared types**: all API shapes go in `@factory/common/src/api/<service>/types.ts` before being used in apps.\n- **Adding a new package**: create a directory, add `package.json` with the workspace name, add its entry to the root `tsconfig.json` paths, then reference it from dependent packages.\n\n## Integration points\n\n- See [apps/web](../apps/web.md) and [apps/desktop](../apps/desktop.md) for the main consumers of `@factory/frontend` and `@factory/core-ui`.\n- See [apps/cli/index.md](../apps/cli/index.md) for the main consumer of `@factory/droid-core` and `@factory/services`.\n- See [overview/architecture.md](../overview/architecture.md) for the full package dependency map.\n- See [how-to-contribute/patterns-and-conventions.md](../how-to-contribute/patterns-and-conventions.md) for UI conventions and `core-ui` usage rules.\n\n## Entry points for modification\n\n- Adding a new primitive component → `packages/core-ui/src/primitives/<Name>/` and export from `packages/core-ui/src/index.ts`.\n- Adding a new tool → `packages/droid-core/src/tools/definitions/` and export from its `index.ts`.\n- Adding a shared API type → `packages/common/src/api/<service>/types.ts` and add an export path to `packages/common/package.json`.\n- Adding a new feature module → `packages/frontend/src/features/<feature>/` and wire routes in `packages/frontend/src/router/createAppRouter.ts`.\n",
