            "content": "# @factory/core-ui — design system\n\n**Active contributors:** Andrei Savin, Ricky S, Nikita Lilichenko, Luke Alvoeiro, Alvin Sng, Eno Reyes\n\n## Purpose\n\n`@factory/core-ui` is the mandatory design system for all web and desktop UI in the Factory monorepo. It provides layout primitives, form controls, overlays, typography, icons, a semantic color system, and design tokens. No consumer may use raw HTML elements like `<div>`, `<button>`, or `<input>` — every interface element must be built from primitives exported by this package or from `@factory/component-library`.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/core-ui/src/\n├── colors/        # Palette definitions and semantic color mappings\n├── fonts/         # Font face declarations\n├── form/          # Higher-order form controls (RadioButtonPills)\n├── hooks/         # useMountEffect and other shared hooks\n├── icons/         # Icon component, Lucide re-exports, custom icons\n├── primitives/    # Box, Flex, Grid, Button, Input, Modal, Toast, etc.\n├── styles/        # global.css (imported once at app root)\n├── tokens/        # Spacing, radius, font-size, z-index, breakpoints\n├── typography/    # Header, Text, TextWithEllipsis components\n└── utils/         # KeyboardShortcut, style-props helpers, platform utils\n```\n\n`packages/core-ui/src/index.ts` is the single public API surface — import everything from `@factory/core-ui`.\n\n## Key abstractions\n\n| Abstraction | Location | Description |\n|-------------|----------|-------------|\n| `Box` | `primitives/Box/Box` | Base layout element backed by a `<div>`; accepts style-prop shorthand |\n| `Flex` | `primitives/Flex/Flex` | `Box` preset with `display: flex` |\n| `Grid` | `primitives/Grid/Grid` | `Box` preset with `display: grid` |\n| `Button` | `primitives/Button/Button` | Pressable element; variants via `ButtonVariant`, sizes via `ButtonSize` |\n| `IconButton` | `primitives/IconButton/IconButton` | Icon-only button with accessible label |\n| `Input` | `primitives/Input/Input` | Controlled text input |\n| `TextArea` | `primitives/TextArea/TextArea` | Controlled multi-line input |\n| `Select` / `SelectItem` | `primitives/Select/Select` | Radix UI select with Factory styling |\n| `Dropdown` / `DropdownItem` | `primitives/Dropdown/Dropdown` | Radix UI dropdown menu |\n| `Modal` | `primitives/Modal/Modal` | Radix UI dialog; variants via `ModalVariant`, sizes via `ModalSize` |\n| `Toast` / `ToastProvider` | `primitives/Toast/Toast` | Radix UI toast notification |\n| `Tooltip` / `TooltipProvider` | `primitives/Tooltip/Tooltip` | Radix UI tooltip |\n| `ScrollArea` | `primitives/ScrollArea/ScrollArea` | Radix UI custom scrollbar |\n| `Collapsible` | `primitives/Collapsible/Collapsible` | Radix UI collapsible section |\n| `Checkbox` | `primitives/Checkbox/Checkbox` | Radix UI checkbox |\n| `Switch` | `primitives/Switch/Switch` | Radix UI toggle switch |\n| `RadioGroup` / `RadioItem` | `primitives/Radio/Radio` | Radix UI radio group |\n| `Tabs` | `primitives/Tabs/Tabs` | Radix UI tabs |\n| `Avatar` | `primitives/Avatar/Avatar` | User avatar with `AvatarSize` enum |\n| `Card` | `primitives/Card/Card` | Surface container |\n| `Loading` | `primitives/Loading/Loading` | Loading indicator |\n| `Alert` | `primitives/Alert/Alert` | Status alert; variants via `AlertVariant` |\n| `Spinner` | `primitives/Spinner/Spinner` | Animated spinner |\n| `Skeleton` | `primitives/Skeleton/Skeleton` | Placeholder skeleton; variants via `SkeletonVariant` |\n| `Skeleton` | `primitives/Skeleton/Skeleton` | Content loading placeholder |\n| `ResponsiveSwitch` | `primitives/ResponsiveSwitch/` | Renders different subtrees based on layout variant |\n| `TerminalDropdown` | `primitives/TerminalDropdown/` | Dropdown styled for terminal contexts |\n| `HatchBackground` | `primitives/HatchBackground/` | Decorative hatched pattern background |\n| `Video` | `primitives/Video/Video` | `<video>` wrapper |\n| `Header` | `typography/Header/Header` | Semantic heading with `HeaderVariant` |\n| `Text` | `typography/Text/Text` | Body text with `TextVariant` |\n| `TextWithEllipsis` | `typography/TextWithEllipsis/` | Single-line truncation with tooltip |\n| `TextWithAnimatedEllipsis` | `typography/TextWithAnimatedEllipsis/` | Animated `...` suffix for loading states |\n| `Icon` | `icons/Icon` | Wrapper around Lucide icons with Factory sizing/coloring |\n| `colors` | `colors/constants` | Full color object: `colors.palettes.*` and `colors.semantics.*` |\n| `spacing`, `radii`, `fontSizes` | `tokens/constants` | Design token maps |\n| `KeyboardShortcut` | `utils/KeyboardShortcut/` | Renders platform-adapted keyboard shortcuts |\n\n## How it works\n\n### Color system\n\nThe palette layer defines six named palettes: **tungsten** (20 neutral grays), **ruby** (red), **mica** (orange), **topaz** (amber), **jade** (green), and **azurite** (blue). Each palette maps numeric indices to hex values.\n\nThe semantic layer maps role names to palette values for both light and dark modes:\n\n| Semantic group | Variants |\n|----------------|----------|\n| `colors.semantics.primary` | `primary-1`, `primary-2`, `primary-10` |\n| `colors.semantics.text` | `default`, `inverted`, `heading`, `subheading`, `muted`, `label`, `success`, `warning`, `error`, `link`, `highlight` |\n| `colors.semantics.surface` | `surface-1` through `surface-5`, `surface-inverted` |\n| `colors.semantics.border` | `border-1` through `border-4` |\n| `colors.semantics.icon` | `icon-accent` |\n\nAlways use semantic tokens in new components. Never hard-code hex values.\n\n### Token system\n\nDesign tokens in `packages/core-ui/src/tokens/constants.ts` cover:\n\n- **`spacing`**: `none`, `xs` (2 px), `sm` (4 px), `md` (8 px), `lg` (12 px), `xl` (16 px), `2xl` (24 px), `3xl` (32 px), `4xl` (64 px)\n- **`radii`**: `none`, `xs`, `sm`, `md`, `lg`, `full`\n- **`fontSizes`**: `3xs` (8 px) → `3xl` (36 px) in rem units\n- **`zIndex`**: `dropdown` (1100), `modalOverlay` (1000), `modalContent` (1001), `tooltip` (2000), `toast` (max int)\n- **Breakpoints**: `COMPACT_BREAKPOINT` (768 px), `MEDIUM_BREAKPOINT` (1024 px), `WIDE_BREAKPOINT` (1600 px)\n- **Media query helpers**: `mediumMediaQuery`, `wideMediaQuery`, `hoverMediaQuery`, `touchMediaQuery`\n\n### Primitives and styled-components\n\nAll primitives are implemented with `styled-components` v6. `Box` accepts a set of style shorthand props (padding, margin, color, background, etc.) defined in `utils/style-props.ts`. `Flex` and `Grid` extend `Box` with preset `display` values.\n\nRadix UI primitives (`@radix-ui/react-*`) provide accessibility and keyboard interaction for interactive components; Factory adds its own visual styling on top.\n\n### Icon system\n\n`packages/core-ui/src/icons/` re-exports all Lucide icons via `lucide-react` as `export * from './lucide/icons'`. Custom icons include `FactoryIcon` (product branding) and MCP server icons (`McpServerIcon`, `hasMcpServerIcon`). The `getCodeIcon` helper maps file extensions to icons. Use the `Icon` wrapper with `IconProps.size` and `IconProps.color` rather than importing Lucide icons directly.\n\n### CSS tokens\n\nThe `build` script (`npm run generate:css-tokens`) outputs CSS custom properties from the token maps. Import `@factory/core-ui/global.css` once at the app root (already done in `packages/frontend/src/router/RootApp.tsx`).\n\n## Integration points\n\n- `apps/web` and `apps/desktop` consume `@factory/core-ui` via `@factory/frontend`, which imports `global.css` in `RootApp.tsx`.\n- `@factory/component-library` builds higher-level chat and diff components on top of core-ui primitives.\n- Storybook runs in `apps/web` (check `apps/web/package.json` for the storybook script) and renders stories for core-ui components in isolation.\n- See [how-to-contribute/patterns-and-conventions.md](../how-to-contribute/patterns-and-conventions.md) for the full list of usage rules.\n\n## Entry points for modification\n\n- Adding a new primitive → create `packages/core-ui/src/primitives/<Name>/` with component, types, and optional enums files, then export from `packages/core-ui/src/index.ts`.\n- Adding a new semantic color variant → update `packages/core-ui/src/colors/types.ts` (variant union) and `packages/core-ui/src/colors/constants.ts` (light/dark values).\n- Adding a new spacing or breakpoint token → edit `packages/core-ui/src/tokens/constants.ts` and update the `SemanticSpacingToken` type if adding a new variant.\n- Adding a Lucide icon wrapper → the icons are auto-exported; custom icons go in `packages/core-ui/src/icons/custom/`.\n",
