            "content": "# Factory platform overview\n\nFactory builds Droid — an AI software engineering agent that runs as an interactive CLI tool. Engineers use it to delegate coding tasks, explore codebases, write tests, review PRs, and ship features. Droid converses in natural language, executes shell commands and file edits, calls external tools via MCP, and manages multi-step autonomous missions.\n\nThis monorepo contains every component of the Factory platform: the CLI, the background daemon, the web and desktop frontends, the backend API, shared packages, infrastructure code, and CI/CD pipelines.\n\n## What's in this repo\n\n| Layer | What it is |\n|---|---|\n| `apps/cli` | The Droid CLI — interactive TUI and non-interactive exec mode |\n| `apps/daemon` | `factoryd`, the background service managing agent sessions |\n| `apps/backend` | Next.js API: auth, sessions, LLM proxy, billing, integrations |\n| `apps/web` | Vite + React web interface for Droid sessions |\n| `apps/desktop` | Electron desktop app wrapping the web interface |\n| `apps/admin` | Internal admin dashboard |\n| `apps/factory-vscode-extension` | VS Code integration |\n| `apps/signal` | Internal messaging/relay service |\n| `packages/droid-core` | AI agent core: tools, LLM streaming, message handling |\n| `packages/common` | Shared types, enums, API contracts, feature flag definitions |\n| `packages/core-ui` | Design system primitives used across all web UIs |\n| `packages/frontend` | Shared React features (sessions, settings, auth, wiki) |\n| `packages/services` | Business logic, plugin management, settings service |\n| `infra/` | OpenTofu (Terraform) infrastructure as code |\n\n## Quick links\n\n- [Architecture](./architecture.md) — how the pieces connect\n- [Getting started](./getting-started.md) — install, build, run\n- [Glossary](./glossary.md) — project-specific terms\n- [CLI](../apps/cli/index.md) — the main product\n- [Daemon](../apps/daemon.md) — session lifecycle manager\n- [Backend](../apps/backend.md) — API service\n- [Packages overview](../packages/index.md) — shared libraries\n- [Features](../features/index.md) — user-facing capabilities\n\n## Tech stack at a glance\n\n| Area | Stack |\n|---|---|\n| CLI & daemon | TypeScript, Bun runtime |\n| CLI TUI | Ink (React for terminals) |\n| Web app | Vite, React 19, TypeScript |\n| Backend & admin | Next.js 15, React 19, TypeScript |\n| Desktop | Electron |\n| State management | Redux Toolkit (web/admin), React hooks (CLI) |\n| Styling | styled-components (web/admin), @factory/core-ui |\n| Auth | WorkOS AuthKit |\n| Billing | Orb |\n| Feature flags | Statsig |\n| LLM providers | Anthropic, OpenAI, Google Gemini |\n| Infrastructure | AWS, OpenTofu |\n| Build system | Turborepo + npm workspaces |\n",
